-h
    use to open this menu and terminate

-c
    use to copy entire output to clipboard

-p
    use to add additional line

-S <request>
    use to add additional line
    about sovetromantica bot.
    request - request line for the bot

-s
    show the contents of copied text
    (only useful when used with --clipboard)

-L <count of lines>
    list maker little program that takes telegram link
    and outputs consecutive other links

-f
	force update tokens
	might help if script is stuck on something

-d
	show debug information
